headline: MSCI (MSCI): Assessing Valuation After Recent Momentum in Share Performance
summary: MSCI (MSCI) recently caught investors’ attention after its performance over the past month saw shares rise by nearly 3%. With steady annual revenue and net income growth, many are watching to see whether this momentum will continue. See our latest analysis for MSCI. Momentum around MSCI has been building again, as reflected by its 6.6% share price return over the past 90 days.
